  "original_title": "19\u0b90 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 22\u0b86\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The 22nd Amendment will supersede the 19th",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Justice Minister Vijayadasa Rajapaksa said that the government has decided to re-amend the 22nd Amendment in order to limit the executive power, remove the issues brought in the 19th Amendment and remove the weak clauses in it and bring a new amendment that surpasses the 19th.",
        "He said this during a press conference held yesterday (28) in Colombo. He further said,",
        "The 22nd Amendment Act has been approved by the Cabinet and gazetted. However the then President Gotabaya Rajapaksa added some annexures to the 22nd Amendment. It was criticized as re-emphasizing executive power.",
        "However, due to the fact that the government has completely changed, I have again proposed an idea to the cabinet to remove the links proposed by the former president and bring back the issues brought in the 19th amendment and to remove the weak clauses in it and bring a new amendment that surpasses the 19th amendment.",
        "The said Bill has been sent to the Cabinet Office. After getting approval from the Cabinet next Monday, the move will be gazetted and tabled in Parliament in the next seven days.",
        "It has been agreed in the cabinet to discuss this with all sides and bring about the amendment of the political system in a manner that is acceptable to all, as well as to form a parliamentary selection committee and create a new political system suitable for the country.",
        "There is no change in the fact that the Ministry of Defense should be with the President, according to this political system, if the Ministry of Defense needs to be changed, it must go to a referendum. He said there was no chance of that now."
      ],
